      <hedline>
        <hl1>CORRECTIONS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of brief travel item on January 7 about HotelsByCity.net (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A brief report in the In Transit column on Jan. 7 about HotelsByCity.net carried incorrect information from a blogger on the site who posted a photograph of the singer Lindsay Lohan. She was standing beside a pool with Harry Morton, the Hard Rock heir, at an unidentified hotel in Maui -- not at a Hard Rock Hotel. (Hard Rock Cafe International has no hotels in Maui.)</p>
      </block>
